# COVID-19 Chest X-Ray Classification

A deep learning project for classifying chest X-ray images into:

- COVID-19
- Normal
- Viral Pneumonia

## Model

Transfer Learning using ResNet50

## Features

- Data Augmentation
- Transfer Learning
- Confusion Matrix
- Classification Report
- Streamlit Deployment

## Dataset

COVID-19 Radiography Dataset

## Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run Training

Open:

```bash
covid_project.ipynb
```

## Run Web Application

```bash
streamlit run covid.py
```

## Results

Validation accuracy approximately 65–75%.

